<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p><strong>Last updated:</strong> 15.01.2026</p>

<h2>1. General Information</h2>
<p>This Privacy Policy applies to the mobile application <strong>Smart_serwis</strong>.</p>
<p>Data Controller: <strong>Piotr Kowal</strong> (private individual)<br>
Contact: <strong>smart.serwis.app@gmail.com</strong></p>
<p>The application is available worldwide.</p>

<h2>2. Data Collected</h2>
<ul>
    <li>phone numbers</li>
    <li>device names</li>
    <li>repair descriptions and service notes</li>
    <li>contact list data (only for selecting a phone number)</li>
    <li>in-app purchase data</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. Purpose</h2>
<p>Data is processed only to manage repairs, facilitate communication, and enable in-app purchases.</p>

<h2>4. Communication</h2>
<p>The application does not automatically send messages or make calls. It only opens system applications with pre-filled data.</p>

<h2>5. Contacts Access</h2>
<p>Contacts access is used only to select a phone number and data is not transmitted externally.</p>

<h2>6. In-App Purchases</h2>
<p>Purchases are handled via Google Play and RevenueCat. No payment data is stored by the app.</p>

<h2>7. Data Storage</h2>
<p>All data is stored locally on the user's device.</p>

<h2>8. Data Sharing</h2>
<p>No personal data is sold or shared except for purchase processing.</p>

<h2>9. User Rights</h2>
<p>Users may access, delete, or restrict processing of their data.</p>

